head() and tail() methods for <epiparam> class

Source: R/epiparam.R
head.epiparam.Rd

head() and tail() methods for <epiparam> class

Usage

# S3 method for epiparam
head(x, ...)

# S3 method for epiparam
tail(x, ...)

Arguments

x

An <epiparam> object.

...

dots Extra arguments passed to or from other methods.

Value

Data frame

Examples
